<div class="page-header">
<div class="page-label">Navigation Architecture</div>
<h1 class="page-title">Sixty Entrances</h1>
<p class="page-subtitle">Eighteen grounds, sixty entrances. Every phrase is a doorway. Multiple entrances lead to the same ground by different paths. The entrance shapes the arrival.</p>
<div class="page-rule"></div>
</div>

<section class="sec" id="grounds">
<div class="sec-title">Primary Entrances<span class="sec-count">18</span></div>
<div class="ground-grid">
<a class="ground-card reveal" href="#"><div class="ground-accent" style="background:#c4956a;"></div><div class="ground-number">01</div><div class="ground-label">The Lobby</div><div class="ground-entrance">Eclipse Prayer Shadow Impossible Mirror</div></a>
<a class="ground-card reveal" href="#"><div class="ground-accent" style="background:#D4A574;"></div><div class="ground-number">02</div><div class="ground-label">Writing</div><div class="ground-entrance">River Delta Dry Creek Without Roof and Walls Bedroom</div></a>
<a class="ground-card reveal" href="#"><div class="ground-accent" style="background:#c4956a;"></div><div class="ground-number">03</div><div class="ground-label">Methodology</div><div class="ground-entrance">Badlands Wonderful Goodness Hole In The Wall</div></a>
<a class="ground-card reveal" href="#"><div class="ground-accent" style="background:#a8c8e0;"></div><div class="ground-number">04</div><div class="ground-label">The Journey</div><div class="ground-entrance">Floating Between Earth and Stone Canyon Basin</div></a>
<a class="ground-card reveal" href="#"><div class="ground-accent" style="background:#D4A574;"></div><div class="ground-number">05</div><div class="ground-label">Essential Ten</div><div class="ground-entrance">Glacial Erratic Stable Sinkhole</div></a>
<a class="ground-card reveal" href="#"><div class="ground-accent" style="background:#a8d4b0;"></div><div class="ground-number">06</div><div class="ground-label">The Witnesses</div><div class="ground-entrance">Limestone Bluff Mouth</div></a>
<a class="ground-card reveal" href="#"><div class="ground-accent" style="background:#B2916C;"></div><div class="ground-number">07</div><div class="ground-label">Good Grounds</div><div class="ground-entrance">Salt Flat Quarry Cave</div></a>
<a class="ground-card reveal" href="#"><div class="ground-accent" style="background:#6a4a7a;"></div><div class="ground-number">08</div><div class="ground-label">Making</div><div class="ground-entrance">Gloriously Grooved Volcanic Caldera</div></a>
<a class="ground-card reveal" href="/portraits"><div class="ground-accent" style="background:#662a1e;"></div><div class="ground-number">09</div><div class="ground-label">The Portraits</div><div class="ground-entrance">Fjord Tool Face Landing</div></a>
<a class="ground-card reveal" href="#"><div class="ground-accent" style="background:#B2916C;"></div><div class="ground-number">10</div><div class="ground-label">The Prayers</div><div class="ground-entrance">Natural Built Then Ruined or Softened Shelter</div></a>
<a class="ground-card reveal" href="#"><div class="ground-accent" style="background:#a8c8e0;"></div><div class="ground-number">11</div><div class="ground-label">The Novel</div><div class="ground-entrance">Tidal Pool Sandbar Sea Turtle Castle</div></a>
<a class="ground-card reveal" href="/the-puppets"><div class="ground-accent" style="background:#c4956a;"></div><div class="ground-number">12</div><div class="ground-label">The Puppets</div><div class="ground-entrance">Permanent to Temporary Underground Fortified Space that has Linear Cracks of Sunlight</div></a>
<a class="ground-card reveal" href="#"><div class="ground-accent" style="background:#7a8ea0;"></div><div class="ground-number">13</div><div class="ground-label">Sound</div><div class="ground-entrance">Peat Bog Notes Cliff</div></a>
